            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Google 推出的 Android 「畫圈搜尋」（Circle to Search）功能，讓 Android 手機用户可以以畫圈方式直接搜尋。現在 iPhone 用家也可以使用類似功能，只需使用 iOS 版最新的 Google app 搭配 Google 以圖搜圖捷徑即可。</p><p>Google 今年一月推出了「Circle to Search」，用户無須再跳轉至搜尋引擎，可以直接在螢幕以畫圈手勢搜尋圖片及文字。現在 iPhone 用家也可以使用類似功能，要使用這個功能，首先你要下載最新的「Google」應用程式，隨後再安裝「捷徑」，簡單設定後無論在網上或是在現實生活中遇到有趣的事，也可以直接使用「以圖搜尋」功能上網搜尋。</p><h2>Step 1 下載／更新 Google 應用程式</h2><p>要在 iPhone 使用「畫圈搜尋」功能，首先要安裝／更新 Google 應用程式。下載連結：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/google/id284815942">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/google/id284815942</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059.jpeg 369w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2>Step 2 允許「Google」App 存取照片</h2><p>下載完成後，開啟 Google 應用程式，點擊下圖綠色框指住的按鍵，允許 Google 存取你的圖片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊上圖框住的按鍵</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「Allow access」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「允許全權取用」</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】跨平台無線傳送檔案，不在家 Android、iOS 傳相片影片到家中電腦</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份證將加入 Apple 錢包，美國以外首個國家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國 4 月 iPhone 銷量增 52%    智能手機銷量按年增長 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Step 3 下載「捷徑」</h2><p>下載完 Google 應用程式後，此時要安裝 Apple 官方「捷徑」應用程式（<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334">下載連結</a>）。如果你的電話已經有這個 App，就可以跳至 Step 4。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449-681x580.jpg" alt="" width="681" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449-681x580.jpg 681w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 681px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲沒有「捷徑」的用家可以先下載這個 Apple 官方應用程式</p><h2>Step 4 設定「捷徑」</h2><p>安裝完成後開啟捷徑，然後點擊右上角的「<b>+</b>」符號，跳頁後按「加入動作」，在「搜尋 App 和動作」位置輸入「Take screenshot」，選擇「拍攝螢幕截圖」。接下來再次在「搜尋 App 和動作」輸入「Google」，點擊</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239127" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「+」符號（綠框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239129" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「加入動作」符號（綠框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239133" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在綠色框處輸入「Take screenshot」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239131" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「拍攝螢幕截圖」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239136" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在此欄目輸入「Google」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊綠色框框住的 Google 字樣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「使用智慧鏡頭搜尋圖片」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239157" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「完成」（綠色框示）</p><h2>Step 4 設定快速開啟「畫圈搜尋」功能</h2><p>倘若要每次開啟「捷徑」才能使用這個功能的話，略嫌有點不方便。要如 Android 般一鍵使用「畫圈搜尋」，我們可以使用 iPhone 的輔助觸控功能，點擊手機後背 2 下即可自動啟用「畫圈搜尋」功能。先開啟設定，選擇「輔助使用」，選擇「觸控」，然後點擊「機背點按」，選擇「使用智慧鏡頭搜尋圖片」，之後你就可以輕拍機背 2 下召喚「畫圈搜尋」功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟「設定」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239170" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「輔助使用」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239171" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1.png 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「觸控」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「機背點按」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「使用智慧鏡頭搜尋圖片」</p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><h2>Step 5 完成</h2><p>現時已完成所有設定，如果你在上網時看到感興趣的圖片，可以輕點機背 2 下，即可召喚「畫圈搜尋」功能。</p><div style="padding: 216.22% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_2548" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/951470981?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>如果你想直接拍攝照片，再利用 Google 智慧鏡頭搜尋，這個捷徑也能夠幫到你。首先開啟「相機」，對準你要搜尋的物品，然後輕點機背 2 下，這樣就可以使用捷徑搜尋你鏡頭拍攝的物品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟相機鏡頭後輕點機背 2 下</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可搜尋相機拍攝到的圖片</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】跨平台無線傳送檔案，不在家 Android、iOS 傳相片影片到家中電腦</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份證將加入 Apple 錢包，美國以外首個國家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國 4 月 iPhone 銷量增 52%    智能手機銷量按年增長 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>總結：前期設定較為繁複　使用非常方便</h2><p>雖然這個捷徑前期設定步驟比較繁複，但小編覺得這個捷徑算是實用，上網時只要看見感興趣的東西，輕點機背 2 下即可搜尋；開啟相機時點擊機背 2 下亦可直接 Google 搜尋相機拍攝到的畫面。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】跨平台無線傳送檔案，不在家 Android、iOS 傳相片影片到家中電腦</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份證將加入 Apple 錢包，美國以外首個國家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中國 4 月 iPhone 銷量增 52%    智能手機銷量按年增長 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/iphone-circle-to-search-by-shortcut/tips-2/">【教學】iPhone 也可「畫圈搜尋」　輕觸機背即可使用 + 即影即 Google</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
